title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update 15 beta - final release?
description:
In this video we will have a look at the 6th beta build of Sim Update 15. Most likely this will also be the final version also known as GA version. The long waited A320 V2 is back and a lot of people were waiting for that one to arrive. Other then that only a few minor fixes are included in this build.
